            <title><![CDATA[Your Mentor]]></title>
            <descriptionText><![CDATA[<font face="helvetica" size="3"><B>Mackenzie “Mack” Miller (Your Mentor)</B> A veteran sales manager and successful relationship builder, Mack is highly respected throughout the company and by customers. A testament to his fierce attention to his customers, a sign on Mack’s desk reads, “This conversation will be interrupted only when a customer calls.” Mack is always ready with a genuine smile and a kind word for everyone he meets. People are often surprised to learn that he is an accomplished skydiver, with more than 100 successful jumps.</font>]]></descriptionText>
